  m_text: "Welcome, traveler.\nYou arrive in Moonveil, a quiet coastal town shrouded
    in mystery.\nIts people have begun to fall into an endless sleep - their dreams
    whispering of something ancient stirring beyond the moons\u2019 light.\n\nIn
    this demo, you can experience the early foundations of Lunaris Legends:\n\u2022
    Test the combat system\n\u2022 Experiment with inventory and equipment\n\u2022
    Complete a few introductory quests\n\u2022 Visit shops and trade with the locals\n\u2022
    Prove your strength in the battle arena\n\nThank you for playing and supporting
    the project!\n- VS&G Team"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 01e43599a655c6443bffaa72c55f3f51, type: 2}
